title: january 4: the newest tallest building
description:
Today on 365 days with mxmtoon, Maia talks about the building and opening of the current tallest building in the world, the Burj Khalifa in Dubai. Then, Maia talks about an all star musical mashup: Kendrick Lamar, SZA, and the acclaimed film Black Panther. Join this episode today and make sure you’re following along with the daily updates @365daysmxmtoon on all platforms.
